Class AgencyCycleDistChargeOwnerView

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.web.producer.agencybill.distributionwizard.AgencyCycleDistChargeOwnerView
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AgencyCycleDistAccountView, AgencyCycleDistCollateralRequirementView, AgencyCycleDistCollateralView, AgencyCycleDistPolicyView

    public abstract class AgencyCycleDistChargeOwnerView
extends java.lang.Object
    AgencyCycleDistChargeOwnerView serves to associate a given ChargeOwner (TAccount) with a list of dist items for display in the AgencyDistributionWizard.
